      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be quantified and reported; discretization error must be below 5% for primary QoI at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (coarse 2.1M, medium 5.4M, fine 12.8M cells). GCI for shear stress scalar (primary hemolysis driver) was 2.3% between medium and fine meshes. Medium mesh selected for production runs. Richardson extrapolation applied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
