      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must use geometry, fluid properties, and operating conditions representative of the COU device and use scenario at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry—the same geometry used in the COU. Blood analog fluid properties matched to 37°C whole blood viscosity. Operating envelope covers all 5 COU flow-speed combinations, confirming high relevance of validation activities."
    },
    {
