      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Simulation setup reviewed by a second analyst prior to production runs. Boundary condition inputs and material property assignments documented in the simulation plan and cross-checked against test data."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
