      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, model form uncertainty quantification is not required; selection of governing equations must be documented.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Reynolds-Averaged Navier-Stokes (RANS) with SST k-omega turbulence closure selected based on published literature for rotary blood pump CFD. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) applied. Model form selection rationale documented in the modeling report."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
