      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal input uncertainty propagation is not required; nominal input values must be traceable to measurements or literature.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Fluid density and viscosity sourced from published blood analog characterization data. Pump geometry dimensions taken from FDA generic pump CAD files. Rotational speed and flow rate boundary conditions set to nominal COU operating points."
    },
    {
