      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Blood analog fluid prepared from a single glycerol-water batch with viscosity verified at 37°C prior to testing. Pump test unit serial number and inspection records documented. Sample representativeness addressed qualitatively in the test report."
    },
